Code preview of the table FAR_PAT

drop table if exists FAR_PAT;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: FAR_PAT */
/*==============================================================*/
create table FAR_PAT
(
ID_PAT int not null comment 'Identificador único para la patología.',
ID_FAR int not null comment 'Identificador único para el fármaco
',
primary key (ID_PAT, ID_FAR)
);

alter table FAR_PAT comment 'Entidad que registra que medicamento es tratamiento para cie';

alter table FAR_PAT add constraint FK_ES_DETECTADA foreign key (ID_PAT)
references PAT (ID_PAT) on delete restrict on update restrict;

alter table FAR_PAT add constraint FK_SE_ASOCIA foreign key (ID_FAR)
references FAR (ID_FAR) on delete restrict on update restrict;
